Move right in to this 3 bedroom cape which also features a front-back Living Room-Dining Room and a 1st floor bedroom.  Enjoy cooking meals in the kitchen with all stainless steel appliances.  Or if you prefer, move outside to the oversized composite rear deck and a fenced spacious back yard, complete with hot tub!!   There are hardwood floors on both levels.  The updated 200 amp electrical service was installed in 2015.  Excellent highway access for commuters or to travel anywhere from Auburn.  This warm and welcoming home is priced to sell and will not last long!  Don't miss out!!  See it NOW or plan on attending the Open House on Sunday, August 6th from   1:00 - 3:00 PM!!
